snippet.title: Pokemon Kanto TCG Hack
snippet.description:
Howdy folks, I decided to do a 48 hour hack of Pokemon TCG for GBC. I modified some decks, changed all the cards in-game, modified some text, and gave all character art and card art a change. Most cards featured in game are from the Gym Heroes/Gym Challenge sets.

If you'd like to play it, the patch can be found here: https://www.mediafire.com/file/18z19ck4gdstrbm/kantotcg.ips/file
